P937: work location is location where persons were active

P81: connecting line is railway or public transport line(s) subject is directly connected to; use as a qualifier to P197

P121: item operated is equipment, installation or service operated by the subject

P461: opposite of is item that is the opposite of this item
P530: diplomatic relation is diplomatic relations of the country

P735: given name is first name or another given name of this person; values used with the property shouldn't link disambiguations nor family names.

P840: narrative location is the narrative of the work is set in this location
P1056: product or material produced is material or product produced by a government agency, business, industry, facility, or process
